                    "title": "Problem Statement",
                    "content": [
                        {
                            "type": "text",
                            "text": "Sort an array of strings so that all anagrams are grouped together. **Example:** ``` Input: [\"eat\", \"tea\", \"tan\", \"ate\", \"nat\", \"bat\"] Output: [ [\"ate\", \"eat\", \"tea\"], [\"bat\"], [\"nat\", \"tan\"] ] ``` **Notes:** - All inputs are lowercase. - Output order does not matter."
                        }
                    ]
                },
